posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'Enjoy quiet community living at the Cottages of White Bear!', 'Our fabulous one, two, and three bedroom floor plans aren’t available often, so don’t miss out!', 'See our spacious homes with updated features, private entry, and walk-in closets for yourself when you schedule your tour today!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Generous Bedroom Closets', '- Standard Electric Kitchen Appliances', '- Some Upgrades To Flooring & Appliances', '- Updated Blinds', '- Ample Counter-Top & Cabinet Space', '- Handicapped Accessible*', '- Master Suite Walk-In Closet *', '- Updated Furnaces & Air-Conditioning Units', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Cottages of White Bear is a 55 or better senior community and participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:8:30AM-5:00PM', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Cottages of White Bear', '4768 Golden Pond Lane', 'White Bear Lake, MN, 55110', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'MqDkef9Vtk8']
